Skowarnki  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Debrzno, within Człuchów County, Pomeranian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  northwest of Debrzno,  west of Człuchów, and  southwest of the regional capital Gdańsk.
